description:
This is a 12 minute workout called 'Elevate Your Start: LiveStrong's 10 Min Beginner Treadmill Run - Follow Along and Thrive!' from the channel IBX Running.
The workout falls under Cardio/Treadmill and Cardio/HIIT.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
You'll need Treadmill for this workout.
The workout has a The Meditative Grind and The Endorphin Wave vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light and Moderate.

Original workout description: Quick and flexible today! Lots of hills, but you can choose if you want to take this workout at a walk, a run, or a combination!

Check out where we got the workout from here: https://www.livestrong.com/article/13776955-10-minute-treadmill-workout/

11:00 minutes of run and recovery intervals

All speeds and inclines are suggestions. Please stay safe and within your comfort zone!
